title: Twisted Wonderland The Comic: Episode of Heartslabyul
description: Enma Yuuken is a high school student who lived an average life until a black carriage suddenly appeared in front of him one day on his way home from club. After seeing it and losing conciousness, he awoke in another world called Twisted Wonderland. Follow his adventures in a magic realm where everyone idolizes classic Disney villains!
author: Sumire Koono
